  "title": "Brand Marketing Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Brand Marketing Executive (Finance Sector)</strong><br /><strong>TVG Management Pte. Ltd.</strong><br /><br /><strong>About TVG Management :</strong><br /><br />TVG Management is a growing financial services firm focused on long-term wealth solutions, leadership development, and sustainable business growth. We work closely with professionals across finance, banking, and insurance, and we are expanding our brand presence to support our next phase of growth.</p><p><strong>Role Overview : </strong></p><p>We are looking for a Brand Marketing Executive to support and strengthen TVG Management’s brand positioning within the financial services industry. This role is ideal for someone who enjoys building brand presence, crafting compelling messages, and executing marketing initiatives that support business growth.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities :</strong></p><ul><li>Develop and execute brand marketing initiatives aligned with TVG Management’s positioning in the finance sector.</li><li>Plan and manage marketing campaigns across digital, social media, and offline channels.</li><li>Create and manage content such as marketing materials, social media posts, and campaign visuals.</li><li>Ensure brand consistency across all touchpoints and communications.</li><li>Support recruitment branding and corporate branding initiatives</li><li>Track and analyse campaign performance and recommend improvements.</li><li>Coordinate with internal stakeholders to support marketing and business objectives.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements :</strong><br /></p><ul><li> Min diploma of any related field. </li><li>1–3 years of experience in branding, marketing, or related roles (finance or professional services is a plus).</li><li>Familiar with social media platforms and relevant marketing tools.</li><li>Strong communication and copywriting skills.</li><li>Creative, organised, and able to manage multiple projects.</li><li>Comfortable working in a fast-paced environment.</li></ul><p><strong>What We Offer :</strong></p><ul><li>Exposure to the financial services and advisory industry.</li><li>Opportunity to shape and grow a brand in a scaling organisation.</li><li>Career development and learning opportunities.</li><li>Supportive and collaborative team environment.</li></ul><p><strong>Interested candidates are welcome to apply.</strong></p>",
